         <abstract id="aspace_2a161a23bf11fa418bbe7dedbbc09856">The collection contains photographs and slides documenting the construction of Trumbull College at Yale, including interior and exterior views.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_70328c994817afab681ecaafc5f48ef3">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_c9eb205c6c53b4ee8ea564a1eff3ee59">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Trumbull College, Yale University, Photographs (RU 609). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_49e0fdaba49d01afae1d3cc07f58e979">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_0e7e08f597b100e6efd61265543ed988">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The materials are arranged in four series: I. Construction Progress Photographs, 1930-1933. II. General Views, 1930-1969. III. Oversize. IV. Slides and transparencies.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_dea8739bfcde0e14b0ce44619639c4fb">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains photographs and slides documenting the construction of Trumbull College at Yale, including interior and exterior views.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
